Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, coreutils
Description: Header files related to Linux kernel version 6.13-rc4
 This package provides kernel header files for version 6.13-rc4, for sites
 that want the latest kernel headers. Please read
 /usr/share/doc/linux-qcom-x1e-headers-6.13-rc4-0/debian.README.gz for details

Package: linux-qcom-x1e-tools-6.13-rc4-0
Build-Profiles: <!stage1>
Architecture: amd64 armhf arm64 ppc64el s390x
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, linux-tools-common
Description: Linux kernel version specific tools for version 6.13-rc4-0
 This package provides the architecture dependant parts for kernel
 version locked tools (such as perf and x86_energy_perf_policy) for
 version 6.13-rc4-0 on
 ARMv8.
 You probably want to install linux-tools-6.13-rc4-0-<flavour>.

